{"word":"ἰαίνω","slug":"ἰαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰαίνω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to heat</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to melt</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be melted</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to warm, cheer</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>fovere</el>, <el>θυμὸν ἰαίνειν</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἐν φρεσὶ θυμὸς ἰάνθη</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>μέτωπον ἰάνθη</el> her brow <i>unfolded</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> rei, <i>to take delight in</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}